// =============================================================================
// SAKURA — SECURITY & DATA AUDIT
// Scope: Flask backend + Angular frontend + bundled Ollama sidecar + Celery + SQLite.
// Target: high-security corporate environment with regulated customer data,
//         on-premise deployment, no outbound internet.
// Methodology: Code review of auth/authz, data boundaries, secrets, deps,
//              network, injection, logging, file IO. Mapped to OWASP ASVS L2 /
//              CWE / NIST 800-53 / ISO 27001 / GDPR controls.
// =============================================================================

